# == Class: php::apache::config
#
# Configure php.ini settings for a PHP SAPI
#
# === Parameters
#
# [*file*]
#   The path to ini file
#
# [*config*]
#   Array of augeas commands, one command per entry
#
# === Variables
#
# No variables
#
